### 1. Add `shared/auth/` — Global Auth State Layer

This is the **only new directory**. It is a thin state-holder layer with no full Clean Architecture sub-layering needed.

#### [NEW] `app/example/lib/src/shared/auth/auth_status.dart`

```dart
/// 全局认证状态枚举
enum AuthStatus { unknown, authenticated, unauthenticated }
```

#### [NEW] `app/example/lib/src/shared/auth/auth_session.dart`

```dart
import 'package:freezed_annotation/freezed_annotation.dart';
import 'auth_status.dart';

part 'auth_session.freezed.dart';

/// 全局认证会话模型（不可变）
@freezed
class AuthSession with _$AuthSession {
  const factory AuthSession({
    @Default(AuthStatus.unknown) AuthStatus status,
    String? userId,
    String? username,
    // 若后续接入真实 token，在此添加 token 字段
  }) = _AuthSession;

  /// 便捷判断：是否已认证
  const AuthSession._();
  bool get isAuthenticated => status == AuthStatus.authenticated;
}
```

#### [NEW] `app/example/lib/src/shared/auth/auth_session_notifier.dart`

```dart
import 'package:riverpod_annotation/riverpod_annotation.dart';
import 'auth_session.dart';
import 'auth_status.dart';

part 'auth_session_notifier.g.dart';

/// 全局认证会话状态管理器
///
/// - features/authentication 在登录/登出成功后写入此 Notifier
/// - 其他 feature 或路由守卫通过 read/watch 此 Provider 获取状态
@riverpod
class AuthSessionNotifier extends _$AuthSessionNotifier {
  @override
  AuthSession build() => const AuthSession();

  /// 设置为已认证（登录成功后调用）
  void setAuthenticated({required String userId, required String username}) {
    state = AuthSession(
      status: AuthStatus.authenticated,
      userId: userId,
      username: username,
    );
  }

  /// 设置为未认证（登出或 session 过期后调用）
  void setUnauthenticated() {
    state = const AuthSession(status: AuthStatus.unauthenticated);
  }
}
```

#### [NEW] `app/example/lib/src/shared/auth/auth_interceptor.dart`

```dart
import 'package:flutter_riverpod/flutter_riverpod.dart';
import 'auth_session_notifier.dart';

/// HTTP 请求拦截器：自动注入认证凭据
///
/// 当后端接入真实 token 后，在此处将 token 写入请求头。
/// 目前仅作为扩展入口保留，供 NetworkModule 配置时使用。
class AuthInterceptor {
  final Ref _ref;
  const AuthInterceptor(this._ref);

  /// 返回当前认证头，若未登录则返回 null
  Map<String, String>? buildAuthHeaders() {
    final session = _ref.read(authSessionNotifierProvider);
    if (!session.isAuthenticated) return null;
    // 示例：return {'Authorization': 'Bearer ${session.token}'};
    return null; // 待真实 token 接入后填充
  }
}
```

